channel.title: Free Stuff
channel.description:
Whenever you find a free vps or free domain, you figure out soon enough that they're fake. I made this topic because i stumbled across like 6 Free VPS' but when i try to confirm my sms, Guess what, they put up an error so you cant activate!
Thoughts on this?
Btw.. i'm not saying im a hobo, im just saying.. what's the point in putting up fake services?
